data.description: Here's the Ying and the Yang on this opportunity Ranch home in Springfield Schools!  On the Ying - We have an updated Roof, 100 amp Electrical, Furnace, and Siding around 9 years ago!  A fenced in .22 Acre Lot gives plenty of room to roam, shed out back too! On the Yang - we have some floors that need replaced / repaired!  So... if you're handy or have some great connections this could be just the opportunity for you!  Updated cupboards in kitchen & countertops! Pantry! All appliances stay for easy move in! Laundry area w/storage! New Window A/C Unit!  Quiet location!  Sold As Is.
